data.description: Newly constructed 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bathroom, 2 car garage home in the Epperson Lagoon area of Wesley Chapel. As a resident, you will have access to the Crystal Lagoon. Overpass Road exit off I75 is nearby making Tampa easily accessible. Tampa Outlet Mall, the Shops and the Krate are few minutes away. This home features an open floor plan with all the bedrooms and loft upstairs along with the laundry room. It has a flex room downstairs near the entrance. The home has solar panels and an electric car port installed. Seller is the listing agent. Call or text to see home.
